{"tid":750892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴app真係冇撚用 幾時執左佢","createTime":"2018-07-21T10:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T04:16:50.000Z","uid":195479,"like":120,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd8491265ccc30ce49156198bd7ba817ab60365","tid":750892,"uid":195479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"話說我都知九巴個apps都流流地  所以今朝早返工前15分鐘預早係度等 <br />\n我真係屌佢老母  個廢鳩app顯示話架巴士就到 <br />\n顯示左一陣之後 連個即將到既提示都冇埋<br />\n咁我心諗：「一定會有延遲」 我咪繼續戇戇鳩鳩係度等<br />\n15分鐘都過撚左去 屌你個閪 我連個巴士車頭都見唔撚到<br />\n個廢鳩app都顯示埋下一架巴士仲有14分鐘就快到<br />\n架巴士到底揸撚左去邊<br />\n搞撚到我死死地咁趕港鐵  <br />\n以後咪撚同我講九巴app好用<br />\n真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一心諗住坐巴士 唔使同人迫港鐵<br />\n到頭來搞到仲趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢app已del<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/164524_b2c0c249ac3052a151957746edbc8026.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F164524_b2c0c249ac3052a151957746edbc8026.png&h=1368d408&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ce94abb39ef675aa030d3d2f8f83d64e2e415a5","tid":750892,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":39,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09433039f6551c08bdc7b72806af933c51f8b083","tid":750892,"uid":50744,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"舊版好好多"},{"pid":"010fd3d7be3d012b626575925323605c5f77c4e0","tid":750892,"uid":195479,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"1ce94abb39ef675aa030d3d2f8f83d64e2e415a5","tid":750892,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":39,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"右邊等你執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31e99e717e7105b6dcdbb330d311a48897fe112","tid":750892,"uid":56561,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"賣 api 比 google maps 好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff994e8359f7495a83732a75b48a59695ab390b","tid":750892,"uid":53730,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"用埋啲支那聽歌app<br />\n抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84db124faf92f91d3fe0a27f96f88c1e734ee016","tid":750892,"uid":56323,"like":4,"dislike":47,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"隻APP除左好撚多廣告之外都幾好用!<br />\n搵客服都好快回應，<br />\n到站時間都好準，可能你旺區成撚日塞車先冇用姐"},{"pid":"0047d5c15cd59633cf1b86f215b772e771d69ca6","tid":750892,"uid":50526,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"有其他 App 都睇到到站時間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">仲要冇廣告</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c6d3cf4cceb37de1a8b0936c18580f97681034a","tid":750892,"uid":76747,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"咪撚用囉<br />\n記著之後咪裝番睇時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9615657fa6521d127c1305c2b4c910a087b4649","tid":750892,"uid":123082,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"先唔講準唔準<br />\n佢老母 九巴咁撚大公司整個app出黎都要落咁多廣告係咪傻撚左<br />\n<br />\n啲廣告可以幫到佢搵幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落廣告都算 你加個款橫額廣告咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n又要整埋全板個款廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你老母平時搭車都趕時間，諗住睇下架車到未，睇下使唔使跑去車站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知一開就彈個全頁式廣告係到阻撚住曬。<br />\n<br />\n咁大間巴士公司好心就專注返係車務收入到，要開源都唔係簡啲咁既雞毛蒜皮既收入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"1184e3f0d6e0826a3128b2aaffbee79f6e5a8121","tid":750892,"uid":27604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"全版廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acf48f2b6a69bbadecb6b319347bbe43e7b8067","tid":750892,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0047d5c15cd59633cf1b86f215b772e771d69ca6","tid":750892,"uid":50526,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"有其他 App 都睇到到站時間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">仲要冇廣告</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"我都係用其他app睇不過有個廣告係低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7694b36900dbe5153a7b2260fb2b85f33a4913fd","tid":750892,"uid":36670,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"試過見到3分鐘 6分鐘 18分鐘<br />\n緊係等6分鐘果班啦<br />\n點撚知3分鐘果班走左之後，6分鐘果班變左11分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌!!!!!"},{"pid":"976b5d2a1ab820c2a1cc4fbe35dc2b1a734ab4a6","tid":750892,"uid":1159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3acf48f2b6a69bbadecb6b319347bbe43e7b8067","tid":750892,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0047d5c15cd59633cf1b86f215b772e771d69ca6","tid":750892,"uid":50526,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"有其他 App 都睇到到站時間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">仲要冇廣告</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"我都係用其他app睇不過有個廣告係低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14